{"tid":1421692,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"終於喺香港上連登都要翻牆!","createTime":"2019-08-06T08:41:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T08:47:01.000Z","uid":7076,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"81a2f6a92f92246fb2334f0b95e96514b70e3615","tid":1421692,"uid":7076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:41:25.000Z","msg":"有香港大學學生對《立場新聞》表示，今日凌晨無法通過港大校內的「HKU」及「eduroam」WIFI 登入 LIHKG討論區（簡稱：連登），畫面分別顯示「The URL you requested has been blocked」及「Your connection is not private」，登入其他網站、包括成人網站，則未受影響，有學生質疑校方是因近日反修例運動而採取的行動，封鎖連登。<br />\n<br />\n大約於今晨 1 時半，有港大學生以需要個人密碼的「HKU」及「eduroam」校內 WIFI 嘗試連結連登討論區，惟兩者均無法連上網站，只有使用由政府管理的「<a href=\"http://Wi-Fi.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FWi-Fi.HK&d=rGhbZie%2F6bi%2FABGI9SBXCudFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=6ad7c016\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Wi-Fi.HK</a> via HKU」WIFI 或個人網絡熱點才能順利連上連登討論區。<br />\n<br />\n有住港大舍堂的學生表示，舍堂內全層的同學均未能使用「HKU」WIFI 連結連登討論區，惟連結 Facebook 甚至成人網站則暢通無阻，亦有學生需要連 VPN 才能登入連登討論區。不少學生在網上發表意見指校方封鎖網站的行為是「封鎖言論自由」、「終於喺香港上連登都要翻牆」，斥責港大的行為「同中國有咩分別」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7-wifi-%E4%BB%8A%E5%A4%A9%E5%87%8C%E6%99%A8%E6%9C%AA%E8%83%BD%E7%99%BB%E5%85%A5%E9%80%A3%E7%99%BB-%E8%A2%AB%E7%96%91%E5%88%BB%E6%84%8F%E5%B0%81%E9%8E%96-%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E8%BD%9F-%E5%90%8C%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%89%E5%92%A9%E5%88%86%E5%88%A5/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7-wifi-%25E4%25BB%258A%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E5%2587%258C%25E6%2599%25A8%25E6%259C%25AA%25E8%2583%25BD%25E7%2599%25BB%25E5%2585%25A5%25E9%2580%25A3%25E7%2599%25BB-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E7%2596%2591%25E5%2588%25BB%25E6%2584%258F%25E5%25B0%2581%25E9%258E%2596-%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25BD%259F-%25E5%2590%258C%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%2592%25A9%25E5%2588%2586%25E5%2588%25A5%2F&d=rGhbZie%2F6bi%2FABGI9SBXCudFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=b879d5d0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7-wifi-%25E4%25BB%258A%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E5%2587%258C%25E6%2599%25A8%25E6%259C%25AA%25E8%2583%25BD%25E7%2599%25BB%25E5%2585%25A5%25E9%2580%25A3%25E7%2599%25BB-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E7%2596%2591%25E5%2588%25BB%25E6%2584%258F%25E5%25B0%2581%25E9%258E%2596-%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25BD%259F-%25E5%2590%258C%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%2592%25A9%25E5%2588%2586%25E5%2588%25A5%2F&h=c27e4795\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7-wifi-%E4%BB%8A%E5%A4%A9%E5%87%8C%E6%99%A8%E6%9C%AA%E8%83%BD%E7%99%BB%E5%85%A5%E9%80%A3%E7%99%BB-%E8%A2%AB%E7%96%91%E5%88%BB%E6%84%8F%E5%B0%81%E9%8E%96-%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E8%BD%9F-%E5%90%8C%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%89%E5%92%A9%E5%88%86%E5%88%A5/</a>"},{"pid":"479de97ba22fbbb75c47eba0a561b40fa07b85b8","tid":1421692,"uid":271064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:42:13.000Z","msg":"wtf 香港黎加?"},{"pid":"8e2e936f8e751d12dc4a14fa305317365134b1d4","tid":1421692,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:45:00.000Z","msg":"下次發夢圍下hku啦"},{"pid":"0202ea442a46def30e47be8933b7bd4920850f80","tid":1421692,"uid":288351,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:47:01.000Z","msg":"事件要反映其實如果政府要封鎖連登其實可以做得到"}]}